author: The Piano Guys
description:
Jon here! This is one of my favorite arrangements I’ve done in a while. I’m really proud of how it turned out and can’t wait for you all to hear it when it releases! If you’re a Piano Guys fan and a K-Pop Demon Hunters fan, I’m confident you’ll love it. And if you’re only a fan of one or the other, I think you’ll still enjoy it too 😉 Let me know in the comments if any parts of this video stood out to you! @Sarahhhhale 

#kpopdemonhunters #goldensong
#thepianoguys #jonschmidt
#pianocover
title: Golden (K-Pop Demon Hunters) | Piano Guys Teaser & Reaction 🎹
